53:29.406 --> 53:31.874
Hey.
- Hey.

53:31.876 --> 53:34.276
Hi, jocelyn.

53:34.278 --> 53:35.945
- Hey, alison.
We missed you at the bonfire.

53:35.947 --> 53:37.546
- Yeah, I bet you did.

53:37.548 --> 53:41.884
- Okay.
