53:41.886 --> 53:43.219
See you tomorrow, cole.

53:43.221 --> 53:45.287
- See you tomorrow, joce.

53:45.289 --> 53:46.889
- Joce?

53:46.891 --> 53:49.692
Fuck her if you want,
but just don't make me watch.

53:49.694 --> 53:50.759
[thud]
cole!

53:50.761 --> 53:52.895
- What?!
- Don't do that.

53:52.897 --> 53:54.863
- Why?
- Because you're scaring me,

53:54.865 --> 53:56.298
