54:12.783 --> 54:15.251
- I know. I know.
Please.

54:17.020 --> 54:19.588
- [sighs]

54:19.590 --> 54:22.591
- I'm sorry.

54:22.593 --> 54:24.994
Like, I just--

54:24.996 --> 54:27.896
It just hurts so much.

54:27.898 --> 54:30.399
Like--

54:36.373 --> 54:38.941
- I know it does, baby.

54:40.610 --> 54:43.946
- Just...Make it stop.

54:50.387 --> 54:52.955
- I don't know how.

55:19.449 --> 55:20.916
Let's go inside.

55:20.918 --> 55:24.787
- No. No.

55:24.789 --> 55:26.722
- Alison.

55:40.537 --> 55:43.005
- Is this what you want?
- Yes.

55:43.007 --> 55:44.940
[groans]

55:44.942 --> 55:47.376
- [grunts]
is it?

55:58.955 --> 56:00.489
- Oh.

56:13.636 --> 56:15.504
Oh, fuck me.

56:17.107 --> 56:19.074
Fuck me.

56:21.378 --> 56:24.713
Oh. Oh.

56:24.715 --> 56:26.382
Oh!

56:26.384 --> 56:29.618
[gasps]

56:29.620 --> 56:32.755
[breathing heavily]

56:32.757 --> 56:34.857
Oh! Oh.

56:38.161 --> 56:41.663
- [grunts]

56:47.604 --> 56:50.873
- Oh, my god.
Oh, my god.

57:00.683 --> 57:03.085
